criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Women;

          -  Adult;

          -  Obese (BMI between 30 and 39,9 Kg/m²).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy or nursing;

          -  Smokers;

          -  Drinkers;

          -  Use of drug or phytotherapic;

          -  Diagnosis of any cronic disease;

          -  Daily consumption of yogurt.
